{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"a6045b80-4be6-45e4-a4b1-daeb40868529","content":"There are no existing files in this directory, so I'll provide the solution directly.\n\n## Converting to Compiled Bindings\n\nAdd `x:DataType` to your `ContentPage` to enable compiled bindings:\n\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\" ?>\n<ContentPage xmlns=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui\"\n             xmlns:x=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml\"\n             xmlns:vm=\"clr-namespace:YourApp.ViewModels\"\n             x:Class=\"YourApp.Views.SettingsPage\"\n             x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\">\n\n    <VerticalStackLayout Padding=\"20\" Spacing=\"15\">\n        <Label Text=\"{Binding Theme}\" />\n        <Switch IsToggled=\"{Binding NotificationsEnabled}\" />\n        <Label Text=\"{Binding FontSize, StringFormat='Font Size: {0}'}\" />\n    </VerticalStackLayout>\n</ContentPage>\n```\n\nThe key change is **`x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\"`** — this tells the XAML compiler the type of the `BindingContext`, so it resolves bindings at compile time instead of using reflection at runtime.\n\n## Catching Binding Errors at Build Time\n\n1. **Enable strict mode** — add this to your `.csproj`:\n\n   ```xml\n   <PropertyGroup>\n     <MauiStrictXamlCompilation>true</MauiStrictXamlCompilation>\n   </PropertyGroup>\n   ```\n\n   This promotes binding warnings (e.g., misspelled property names) to **build errors**.\n\n2. **What it catches:** If you type `{Binding Themee}` (typo), the build fails with an error like:\n   ```\n   XC0045: Binding: Property \"Themee\" not found on \"SettingsViewModel\"\n   ```\n\n3. **Opting out locally** — if you need a dynamic binding on one element, use `x:DataType=\"\"` to disable compiled bindings for that subtree.\n\n**Summary:** `x:DataType` enables compile-time validation of `{Binding}` paths, and `MauiStrictXamlCompilation` ensures mismatches fail the build rather than silently breaking at runtime.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"d224a891-02f3-4527-b7fd-66d5f1b81e69","outputTokens":556,"requestId":"503F:2EF3EB:1D631B1:2060AF0:69FA8F77"},"id":"0f96e49e-83a1-46cf-ad06-c8c11f7c72b6","timestamp":"2026-05-06T00:46:58.165Z","parentId":"99cc5bc7-5fdc-44c5-9be6-527329ef445f"}
